snippet: While Serena Williams has been the most dominant player of her generation, she still has time to better her rank among the women’s tennis stars who came before her.
lead_paragraph: While Serena Williams has been the most dominant player of her generation, she still has time to better her rank among the women’s tennis stars who came before her.

headline.seo: Dominant Serena Williams Still Has Time to Build on Legacy
headline.main: Dominant in Her Era, Serena Still Has Time to Build on Legacy
